2. Calculate the sum of min_x and max_x (this will give the x-coordinate of the line of reflection).
3. Iterate through the points again and check if the reflection point is in the set of points (using the calculated sum from step 2).
4. If all reflection points exist in the set, return true. Otherwise, return false.
